  <brief_title>Bed Rest, Alternate Daily Fasting and Incretin Effect</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Study on the Incretin Effect, Cognitive Function and Controlled Fasting During Bed Rest in Healthy Male Volunteers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
